    {
      "id": "PopularPost99966",
      "post_content": "EDIT: @wontongsoup13 - please read my post carefully. I didn't say \"bounce it with o-ring\" I said \"a la Oblivion Ring\" (\"a la\" is a latin phrase for those among you who don't have a book learnin' edumafication that means \"like,\" \"similar to,\" or \"reminiscent of\"). In other words, I was saying \"this card's mechanism is similar to o-ring's and thus provides a similar opportunity.\" Nowhere do I say \"bounce it with o-ring.\" Geez!  \n  \n\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*\\*  \n  \nAmping this up for modern creature power it should have been 2/4 (take it out of bolt range) and exiled two lands on its ETB trigger. I'd even pay ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) for this if they gave it that.  \n  \nInterestingly enough, you can cheat this effect a la [Oblivion Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Ring) by bouncing the Petravark in response to its ETB trigger. The bounce resolves first and since no land has yet been exiled, the LTB trigger fizzles, then the ETB land is exiled. Check the rulings on O-ring. Totally legal even if it feels so... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Paleopaladin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost99966\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">EDIT:  @wontongsoup13 - please read my post carefully.  I didn't say \"bounce it with o-ring\" I said \"a la Oblivion Ring\" (\"a la\" is a latin phrase for those among you who don't have a book learnin' edumafication that means \"like,\" \"similar to,\" or \"reminiscent of\").  In other words, I was saying \"this card's mechanism is similar to o-ring's and thus provides a similar opportunity.\"  Nowhere do I say \"bounce it with o-ring.\"  Geez!<br/><br/>****************************************<br/><br/>Amping this up for modern creature power it should have been 2/4 (take it out of bolt range) and exiled two lands on its ETB trigger.  I'd even pay <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> for this if they gave it that.<br/><br/>Interestingly enough, you can cheat this effect a la <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Ring\">Oblivion Ring</a> by bouncing the Petravark in response to its ETB trigger.  The bounce resolves first and since no land has yet been exiled, the LTB trigger fizzles, then the ETB land is exiled.    Check the rulings on O-ring.  Totally legal even if it feels so... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 99966)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy31075\">Paleopaladin</span>\r\n                                (12/25/2010 11:56:27 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
