      "id": "PopularPost118131",
      "post_content": "You can't bounce it with O-ring in response to the trigger because O-ring is an enchantment. You can, however, use [Path to Exile](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Path to Exile), [Swords to Plowshares](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Swords to Plowshares), or any other instant removal for that effect to work. But I'd rather use [Realm razer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Realm razer) instead if I wanted some land sweeping effect",
      "posted_by": "wontongsoup13",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost118131\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">You can't bounce it with O-ring in response to the trigger because O-ring is an enchantment. You can, however, use <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Path to Exile\">Path to Exile</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Swords to Plowshares\">Swords to Plowshares</a>, or any other instant removal for that effect to work. But I'd rather use <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Realm razer\">Realm razer</a> instead if I wanted some land sweeping effect</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36186\">wontongsoup13</span>\r\n                                (11/25/2010 1:44:38 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Star